Red Lanterns (000 - 033) (2011 - Ongoing) (Digital) (Empire)


One of "The New 52" comics that were launched by DC in September 2011 to relaunch their universe. This is the first Red Lanterns series, although the group first appeared three years earlier and starred in various Green Lantern publications. The series is written by Peter Milligan (better known for his work in Vertigo at DC) and drawn by Ed Benes.
